                        <td>
                        
                            <p><strong>I&#39;m 13. In a world ridden with so much hate, and disconnect; How do I live life to its absolute fullest, and not waste my potential? Especially as a creative. Also, what is a great way to spiritually enrich myself? in general, and in my creative work.</strong><br/>
RUBEN, MELBOURNE, AUSTRALIA</p>

